Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.44,0:22:48.68,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}kaze ni ubawareta wake janai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.44,0:22:48.68,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}We weren't spirited away on the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.92,0:22:52.96,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}katamichi bun no yuuki de bokura
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.92,0:22:52.96,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}We knew we could never return, and found the courage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.39,0:22:59.01,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}higeki wo ukeireru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.39,0:22:59.01,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}to accept the hardship
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.73,0:23:03.89,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}kokoro ga koko ni atta hazu no kuudou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.73,0:23:03.89,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}There's an emptiness where my heart used to be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.23,0:23:06.90,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}motto boku ga ookikereba
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.23,0:23:06.90,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}If only I was stronger
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.90,0:23:12.53,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}kimi wo mirai wo sukueta darou ka
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.90,0:23:12.53,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}I could have saved you, and our future...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.53,0:23:19.90,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}taisetsu na hito wo mamoru sube ga tatta hitotsu shika motanai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.53,0:23:19.90,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}I only know of one way to keep the people I love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.90,0:23:26.19,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}sonna anata ga haguretadayou sora
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.90,0:23:26.19,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}And you left me and disappeared into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.73,0:23:33.94,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}anata ijou no hito ni deaenai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.73,0:23:33.94,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}I'll never find anyone like you again
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.42,0:23:40.29,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}tsuki ni aragau nagai furea
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.42,0:23:40.29,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}A long flare reaches out against the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.94,0:23:47.09,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}hajimaru mo sezu owaru monogatari
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.94,0:23:47.09,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}The story ends before it could even begin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.48,0:23:51.18,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}kizutsukiuru yawarakasa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.48,0:23:51.18,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}So soft, so fragile
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.55,0:23:54.52,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}tojikometa senritsu kanaderu hodo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.55,0:23:54.52,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}I will call up the melody locked away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.85,0:24:00.53,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}utau hodo kowareru hodo ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.85,0:24:00.53,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}And sing it until I destroy myself
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.97,0:24:08.34,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}anata ga koishii
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.97,0:24:08.34,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}That's how much I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.29,0:00:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The circle of life turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:00:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our souls are born over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.29,0:01:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They experience grief over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.59,0:01:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that grief goes to the arms of God in Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.77,0:01:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.69,0:01:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the beautiful law of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.35,0:01:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, his soul has left the realm of law for something higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For we do not have the last son's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I say to you that Altair must not die  {timing check}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.74,0:01:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without seeing even a glimpse of its future.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have nothing to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.56,0:01:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last son has shown us the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has shown us that we live in a time of miracles!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.02,0:01:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Altair has no future. Its days are numbered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:02:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Ianthe's power is becoming unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't keep them in the dark forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.05,0:02:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage! What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just spreading the great news to the flock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.06,0:02:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sacrificed Jin for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.99,0:02:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He gave much to the world of Altair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.48,0:02:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His life was a fair price to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.65,0:02:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to deal a great blow to the Rare Iguras' nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We obtained a great deal of direct data on the true Eve candidates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.23,0:02:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the reborn Wings of the Sun finally revealed itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.38,0:02:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin's soul would be filled with joy if it knew what it brought us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it will be reborn in the first of Altair's new generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what you really wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin, what I... what Altair has done can never be forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{no op}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We'll be taking them to the graveyard in Neo-Stanley.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.21,0:03:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{under conversation}The boat will arrive at 2:00. I want everyone there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:30.66,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Where's Yunoha?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:32.23,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}She won't come out of her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or turn visible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.46,0:03:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she going to shut herself in forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how she feels, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I lost someone I loved, I'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yunoha...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:03:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono Suzushiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.93,0:04:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High Commander Fudo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like him at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.44,0:04:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring Yunoha Thrul out of her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to leave her alone for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.20,0:04:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This school's duty is to foster Union, a positive bond that connects people together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None can be allowed to drown selfishly alone in their own sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you call that selfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten Yunoha's Element power? The power to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the wake of Jin Muso's death, her power may go out of control...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she could erase herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed.{one of them Japanese "verb only" sentences so I'm guessing}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.01,0:05:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yunoha, may I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.25,0:05:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might need something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to if you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just leave it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yunoha's aura is getting fainter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what can I possibly say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin asked me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He asked me to go with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I'd gone, Jin wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no... it's getting even fainter now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.80,0:05:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really going to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Yunoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to... to say goodbye to Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.16,0:06:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then don't say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to say goodbye to you, or to Jin either!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.64,0:06:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Yunoha. You're a precious friend to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:07:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, you're on Jin's world?{i dunno if he knows for sure or if he's asking}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... want to...{assuming anata o is like I WANT TO SEE YOU}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.07,0:07:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last the students are learning how grateful they \Nshould be to the place we put our lives on the line for,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the classmates we've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell! We're talking about peoples' lives{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.71,0:08:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've decided to quit school and go back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.39,0:08:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how much you care about your duty?{i hate this line, reflit: "Is that what your resolve is?"}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.01,0:08:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We Elements have been chosen to fight for this planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you forget what an honor that{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.06,0:08:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.65,0:08:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you stand this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been through so much training and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy, not you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naw, I'm staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone has to stick around or we're all doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll all be sucked into that big hole in the sky. {timing check}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna fall into someone else's hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy W. Hol.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dig holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.17,0:09:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All these holes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these holes for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:09:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The planet Altair...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin Muso came from another planet called Altair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Altair...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.03,0:10:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the data Jin left us, we have ascertained Altair's intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.05,0:10:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are kidnapping female Elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The war with Altair will only become more intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As it goes on, more may find themselves buried beneath this earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to prepare you to stand up to the challenge of this war,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will be buried!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be buried? Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I name it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Training of the Grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why? We just \Nburied our classmates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.99,0:11:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want to \Nbe buried in any hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a grave, of all holes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, isn't this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.08,0:11:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say such things when we're all still in pain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each of you is bound by your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you sleep with the dead, the force of your lives will expand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attachment, wickedness, love, stubbornness, hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These thoughts form the links of a chain that shackles each of your souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, just once, you must experience death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Death? {missing line}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will journey to the very edge of life, then return.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.47,0:12:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you discover in your temporary death?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must find out for yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sounds fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already on my way there myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my death is soon to come, I may as well rehearse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Shrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yunoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.56,0:12:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be with Jin, just for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a deep hole. I'll have to fill it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Filling a hole I worked so hard on feels like dying anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.32,0:12:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For you, that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.49,0:12:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eye looks like it can see through everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's also all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dark. I can't see a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so quiet. It's like complete silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is sound here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of the bugs crawling through the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.62,0:13:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The creatures that squirm through the dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel the worms creeping at me, trying to get me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to... I'm going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to turn into dust and break apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:14:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body is rotting away...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rot away... and return to the earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.50,0:14:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where I'll be one with Jin again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so scared... I'm going to go back to the earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I'll never see the surface again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.70,0:14:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be afraid of this hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.63,0:14:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.23,0:14:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.34,0:14:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well. The little Wingless are struggling in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura, you want to join them, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To take the same journey to Hades?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:15:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest in peace, Kagura...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.51,0:15:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard it gets, I can't leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy dug this hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.80,0:15:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dug this hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember that, I won't be scared.{olol}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I can't see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.77,0:15:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even through my Prophecy of Despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Mikono is the reincarnation of Sylvie...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.97,0:15:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then she's not going to choose you, Amata.{this should be written so it sounds less victorous because she sounds like she's feeling really bad for Amata}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She left me behind, and I wanted to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.13,0:16:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.16,0:16:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Jin's not in this world anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I don't want to be in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yunoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.42,0:16:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yunoha's aura is vanishing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata's power of flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zessica's power of distortion{捻る, actually involves twisting or distorting, take that how you want}{tbh distortion sounds like an actual power thing force doesn't???}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrade's sound. Cayenne's despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Yunoha's power of erasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their thoughts are going out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.05,0:16:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it continues...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Yunoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally became friends! We finally connected!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.82,0:17:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.55,0:17:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.86,0:17:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm born again, I'll be abandoned again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be abandoned by anyone ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.66,0:17:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata... Amata is going to be abandoned...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough. I don't want to live anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay here with Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be born again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.90,0:17:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being alive and alone is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.72,0:17:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To live.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all being stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono Suzushiro, this is your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.99,0:18:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ending of life isn't the only death humans experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like how we shed hair and lose teeth,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the cells in our body, heart, and soul are always dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moment by moment by moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moment by moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we are bound to our old, dead selves, if we keep them with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we are divided and cut off from the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono Suzushiro, your power is to connect those who are so divided once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My power is to connect?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. To reach out to those who are attached to their old selves
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and transform their dead into nourishment.{I don't fully understand this but only insofar as it's ZEN saying weird stuff}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the tendrils of a mushroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hidden within the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.94,0:19:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You connect all the fragmented souls together as they dangle between life and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All this time, these twelve thousand years, I've loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight thousand years from the time that I met you, my love will be stronger than ever before.{Jin QUOTING LYRICS FROM BEYOND THE GRAVE}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.76,0:19:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was always alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't care about anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin, it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.14,0:19:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yunoha, when I met you, for the first time I wanted to connect with someone.{this is a long-ass line (19:35~-19:45~) but I don't really know how to break it up without it sounding awful}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't stop living.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yunoha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the rest of you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized that I'm not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,aren't just our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,aren't just our own...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our lives can go beyond life and death...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and connect!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The earth is so warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're being cradled by the dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'm a baby being held at my mom's breast again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.29,0:20:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd never been born, I wouldn't be here to experience this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd never been born, I wouldn't have met anyone here. I wouldn't have met Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.88,0:20:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing scary outside of this hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be danger, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.70,0:21:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there'll be the same warmth I feel in this hole!{you know this sounds dirty but I'm going to leave it as it is}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.48,0:21:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That warmth will always come with pain and suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.89,0:21:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are sounds that must be played from the edge of death and rebirth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.58,0:21:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.01,0:21:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be here, waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you are going to be born again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.67,0:21:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll be waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.23,0:21:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As time flows on, we are all being born moment by moment and reborn moment by moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The instant that nothing becomes something...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.65,0:21:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when a heart is there to experience the instant of now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.79,0:22:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is when thoughts are truly in Union.{fyi this entire sequence is an enormous fucking kanji/Aquarion joke and I have to go kill someone}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.88,0:22:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.67,0:22:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.20,0:22:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.66,0:24:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being reborn from the earth gave those kids quite a power up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.33,0:24:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better step up my game!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.24,0:24:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like my old taser is due for an upgrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{^tlnote "my usual biribiri will become a guringurin no winwin" I don't care what the sound effects are but it sounds like he might replace it for a vibroblade?}
